<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Jared Henriques</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Builder, dad, optimist. Be a good human. Do good work. Make things better." />
		<style>
			@font-face {
				font-family: 'Apercu';
				src: url('/fonts/apercu-regular.woff2') format('woff2'),
					 url('/fonts/apercu-regular.woff') format('woff');
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			@font-face {
				font-family: 'Apercu';
				src: url('/fonts/apercu-medium.woff2') format('woff2'),
					 url('/fonts/apercu-medium.woff') format('woff');
				font-weight: 500;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				font-size: 18px;
			}

			body {
				font-family: 'Apercu', -apple-system, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.7;
				color: #2c2c2c;
				background: #f8f6f3;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				padding: 2rem;
				transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
			}

			main {
				max-width: 480px;
				width: 100%;
			}

			.bio {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.bio p {
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			}

			.bio a,
			.bio a:visited,
			.bio a:link {
				color: inherit;
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}

			.bio a:hover {
				color: #c45d3a;
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.bio .tagline {
				font-style: italic;
				color: #6b6b6b;
				margin-top: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			.links {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 1.25rem;
			}

			.links a {
				color: #6b6b6b;
				text-decoration: underline;
				text-underline-offset: 3px;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				transition: color 0.2s;
			}

			.links a:hover {
				color: #c45d3a;
			}

			/* Mobile */
			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				html {
					font-size: 17px;
				}
				body {
					padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
				}
			}

			/* Dark mode */
			@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
				body {
					background: #1a1918;
					color: #e8e4dc;
				}

				.bio a:hover {
					color: #e89b7b;
				}

				.bio .tagline {
					color: #9a9590;
				}

				.links a {
					color: #9a9590;
				}

				.links a:hover {
					color: #e89b7b;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<section class="bio">
				<p>Hey, I'm Jared Henriques.</p>
				<p>I ran a <a href="https://renga.co" target="_blank">branding studio</a>, now I'm at <a href="https://maplebilling.com" target="_blank">Measure</a>.</p>
				<p>Moved to Victoria, BC with my wife and two kids. Right now, I'm thinking a lot about raising kids and building a business in the age of AI.</p>
				<p class="tagline">Be a good human. Do good work. Make things better.</p>
			</section>

			<nav class="links">
				<a href="/writing">Writing</a>
				<a href="https://x.com/jaredhenriques" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
				<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jaredhenriques" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
				<a href="mailto:hey@jared.is">Email</a>
			</nav>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
